1962;;Life for Ruth;;British;;Basil Dearden;;Michael Craig, Patrick McGoohan;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Life_for_Ruth;;John Harris finds himself ostracized and placed on trial for allowing his daughter Ruth to die. His religious beliefs forbade him to give consent for a blood transfusion that would have saved her life. Doctor Brown is determined to seek justice for what he sees as the needless death of a young girl.